{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1480,"text":"I'm a textile artist"},{"time":3080,"text":"most widely known for starting\nthe yarn bombing movement."},{"time":6080,"text":"Yarn bombing is when you take\nknitted or crocheted material"},{"time":9040,"text":"out into the urban environment,\ngraffiti-style --"},{"time":11400,"text":"or, more specifically,"},{"time":12640,"text":"without permission and unsanctioned."}]},{"cues":[{"time":14960,"text":"But when I started this over 10 years ago,"},{"time":17840,"text":"I didn't have a word for it,"},{"time":19400,"text":"I didn't have any\nambitious notions about it,"},{"time":21560,"text":"I had no visions of grandeur."},{"time":23120,"text":"All I wanted to see was something\nwarm and fuzzy and human-like"},{"time":27520,"text":"on the cold, steel, gray facade\nthat I looked at everyday."}]},{"cues":[{"time":31320,"text":"So I wrapped the door handle."},{"time":33560,"text":"I call this the Alpha Piece."},{"time":35960,"text":"Little did I know that this tiny piece\nwould change the course of my life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":40040,"text":"So clearly the reaction was interesting."},{"time":42000,"text":"It intrigued me and I thought,\n\"What else could I do?\""},{"time":44548,"text":"Could I do something in the public domain\nthat would get the same reaction?"},{"time":48760,"text":"So I wrapped the stop sign\npole near my house."},{"time":51880,"text":"The reaction was wild."},{"time":53320,"text":"People would park their cars"},{"time":55400,"text":"and get out of their cars and stare at it,"},{"time":57800,"text":"and scratch their heads and stare at it,"},{"time":59760,"text":"and take pictures of it\nand take pictures next to it,"},{"time":62280,"text":"and all of that was really exciting to me"},{"time":64280,"text":"and I wanted to do every stop sign pole\nin the neighborhood."},{"time":67320,"text":"And the more that I did,\nthe stronger the reaction."}]},{"cues":[{"time":70800,"text":"So at this point I'm smitten."},{"time":72320,"text":"I'm hooked."},{"time":73600,"text":"This was all seductive."},{"time":74880,"text":"I found my new passion"},{"time":76640,"text":"and the urban environment\nwas my playground."}]},{"cues":[{"time":79760,"text":"So this is some of my early work."},{"time":83040,"text":"I was very curious about this idea\nof enhancing the ordinary,"},{"time":86080,"text":"the mundane, even the ugly,"},{"time":87840,"text":"and not taking away its identity\nor its functionality"},{"time":91520,"text":"but just giving it a well-tailored\nsuit out of knitting."},{"time":94920,"text":"And this was fun for me."},{"time":96680,"text":"It was really fun\nto take inanimate objects"},{"time":98960,"text":"and have them come to life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":101440,"text":"So ..."},{"time":102880,"text":"I think we all see the humor in this,"},{"time":104760,"text":"but --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":106000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":107120,"text":"I was at a point where\nI wanted to take it seriously."},{"time":109840,"text":"I wanted to analyze it."},{"time":111120,"text":"I wanted to know why I was letting\nthis take over my life,"},{"time":113880,"text":"why I was passionate about it,"},{"time":115360,"text":"why were other people\nreacting so strongly to it."},{"time":117920,"text":"And I realized something."},{"time":119800,"text":"We all live in this\nfast-paced, digital world,"},{"time":122720,"text":"but we still crave and desire\nsomething that's relatable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":126680,"text":"I think we've all become desensitized"},{"time":129440,"text":"by our overdeveloped\ncities that we live in,"},{"time":132040,"text":"and billboards and advertisements,"},{"time":134840,"text":"and giant parking lots,"},{"time":136480,"text":"and we don't even complain\nabout that stuff anymore."},{"time":139360,"text":"So when you stumble upon"},{"time":140640,"text":"a stop sign pole\nthat's wrapped in knitting"},{"time":143000,"text":"and it seems so out of place"},{"time":144720,"text":"and then gradually -- weirdly --"},{"time":146600,"text":"you find a connection to it,"},{"time":148440,"text":"that is the moment."},{"time":149680,"text":"That is the moment I love"},{"time":150920,"text":"and that is the moment\nI love to share with others."}]},{"cues":[{"time":154280,"text":"So at this point, my curiosity grew."},{"time":157440,"text":"It went from the fire hydrants\nand the stop sign poles"},{"time":160240,"text":"to what else can I do with this material."},{"time":162217,"text":"Can I do something big\nand large-scale and insurmountable?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":166240,"text":"So that's when the bus happened."},{"time":171240,"text":"This was a real game changer for me."},{"time":173280,"text":"I'll always have a soft spot\nin my heart for this one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":176120,"text":"At this point, people\nwere recognizing my work"},{"time":178320,"text":"but there wasn't much out there"},{"time":179840,"text":"that was wrapped in knitting\nthat was large-scale,"},{"time":182240,"text":"and this definitely was the first\ncity bus to be wrapped in knitting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":185520,"text":"So at this point, I'm experiencing,"},{"time":187280,"text":"or I'm witnessing something interesting."},{"time":189360,"text":"I may have started yarn bombing\nbut I certainly don't own it anymore."},{"time":192800,"text":"It had reached global status."},{"time":194360,"text":"People from all over the world\nwere doing this."},{"time":196575,"text":"And I know this because I would travel\nto certain parts of the world"},{"time":199790,"text":"that I'd never been to,"},{"time":200981,"text":"and I'd stumble upon a stop sign pole\nand I knew I didn't wrap it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":204139,"text":"So as I pursued\nmy own goals with my art --"},{"time":208280,"text":"this is a lot of my recent work --"},{"time":211160,"text":"so was yarn bombing."},{"time":212400,"text":"Yarn bombing was also growing."},{"time":213880,"text":"And that experience showed me\nthe hidden power of this craft"},{"time":218240,"text":"and showed me"},{"time":220000,"text":"that there was this common language\nI had with the rest of the world."},{"time":225360,"text":"It was through this granny hobby --"},{"time":227640,"text":"this unassuming hobby --"},{"time":229800,"text":"that I found commonality with people"},{"time":232720,"text":"that I never thought\nI'd have a connection with."}]},{"cues":[{"time":236280,"text":"So as I tell my story today,"},{"time":238920,"text":"I'd also like to convey to you"},{"time":240400,"text":"that hidden power can be found\nin the most unassuming places,"},{"time":243840,"text":"and we all possess skills\nthat are just waiting to be discovered."}]},{"cues":[{"time":247600,"text":"If you think about our hands,\nthese tools that are connected to us,"},{"time":250800,"text":"and what they're capable of doing --"},{"time":253200,"text":"building houses and furniture,"},{"time":254880,"text":"and painting giant murals --"},{"time":256480,"text":"and most of the time\nwe hold a controller or a cell phone."},{"time":260160,"text":"And I'm totally guilty of this as well."},{"time":262760,"text":"But if you think about it,"},{"time":264080,"text":"what would happen\nif you put those things down?"},{"time":266320,"text":"What would you make?\nWhat would you create with your own hands?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":270040,"text":"A lot of people think\nthat I am a master knitter"},{"time":272360,"text":"but I actually couldn't knit\na sweater to save my life."},{"time":275440,"text":"But I did something\ninteresting with knitting"},{"time":277600,"text":"that had never been done before."}]},{"cues":[{"time":279440,"text":"I also wasn't \"supposed to be\" an artist"},{"time":281920,"text":"in the sense that I wasn't\nformally trained to do this --"},{"time":285360,"text":"I'm a math major actually."},{"time":287000,"text":"So I didn't think\nthis was in the cards for me,"},{"time":289880,"text":"but I also know that I didn't\nstumble upon this."},{"time":292840,"text":"And when this happened to me,\nI held on tight,"},{"time":295320,"text":"I fought for it and I'm proud to say\nthat I am a working artist today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":300040,"text":"So as we ponder the future,"},{"time":303280,"text":"know that your future\nmight not be so seamless."},{"time":305495,"text":"And one day, you might\nbe as bored as I was"},{"time":308520,"text":"and knit a door handle\nto change your world forever."}]},{"cues":[{"time":311920,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":313160,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}